          {
            "allowLineSplit": true,
            "content": "The right-aligned float anchors at the text cursor the moment its element is encountered in the child list. Subsequent lines pour into the remaining column to its left — the classic magazine treatment, water parting around a stone. The lineLayoutResolver is called once per line, querying the SpatialMap for available horizontal intervals at that line’s Y coordinate in story space.",
            "keepWithNext": false,
            "kind": "flow-block",
            "overflowPolicy": "clip",
            "pageBreakBefore": false,
            "source": {
