            "content": "The slate-gray banner above demonstrates top-bottom wrap: no text runs alongside it; the full column clears above and below. The cursor advances past the image bottom before any text is placed. Wide pull quotes, full-width dividers, and chapter ornaments are the natural candidates for this mode.",
