          {
            "allowLineSplit": true,
            "content": "A centered float carves two equal intervals from each line it occupies. The resolver fills the left interval first, then immediately continues into the right interval at the same baseline — a single unbroken token stream flowing around both flanks of the obstacle simultaneously. The text narrows on each side for the lines that coincide with the ornament, then springs back to full measure once the float is cleared.",
            "keepWithNext": false,
            "kind": "flow-block",
            "overflowPolicy": "clip",
            "pageBreakBefore": false,
            "source": {
